and identify the needs it would address; 33
(2) A plan to develop a learning lab on the property. 34
(D) As used in this section, "learning lab" means a 35
dedicated space within a facility designed for educational 36
activities that focus on teaching new skills, promoting 37
knowledge of health and wellness, or providing technology 38
training in an accessible setting for engagement by all members 39
of the community. 40
